text: Narendra Kumar Swain (18 December 1939 - 7 September 2020) was an Indian politician. He was a member of the Rajya Sabha from Odisha between 2015 to 2020. He was a member of the Biju Janata Dal. He was born in Odisha. Swain died on 7 September 2020 in Odisha, aged 80.Former MP Narendra Swain passes away ==References== Category:1939 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Odisha Category:Members of the Rajya Sabha
